c4 Tortuga Trading Post

Captain is a person | description A pirate captain seeking fence and supply
Innkeeper is a person | description Runs the alehouse, knows everyone's business

TradingPost is a system | description The Tortuga marketplace
  -Sells plunder [silver]-> Captain
  -Buys provisions [silver]-> Captain

FenceNetwork is a system | description Discreet buyers of stolen goods
  -Routes high-value cargo [coded letters]-> TradingPost

PortAuthority is a system | description Records and tariffs
  -Loose enforcement [parchment]-> TradingPost

Tavern is a system | description Where deals get done
  -Trades gossip for ale [whispers]-> Innkeeper
  -Steers customers [whispers]-> TradingPost
